  gt() %>%
  tab_header(
    title = md("**General Information (n=105)**")

  cols_label(
    Sex = "Sex",
    Count = "Count",
    `Mean Age` = "Mean Age",
    `Standard Deviation` = "St Dev",
    `Minimum Age` = "Min Age",
    `Maximum Age` = "Max Age"
  )
